uct%20studio%20Butterfly%20Effect%20and%20drew%20global%20attention%20after%20saying%20it%20had%20designed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-manus-ai-meta-acquisition-chinese-startup-singapore-agent-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bgeneral-purpose%26quot%3B%20AI%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20conduct%20tasks%20with%20limited%20human%20supervision.%20In%20mid-2025%2C%20the%20startup%20relocated%20to%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Meta%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-acquires-ai-startup-manus-expand-general-purpose-ai-agents-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eacquire%3C%2Fa%3E%20Manus%20and%20sever%20its%20ties%20with%20China%20completely.%20The%20deal%20reportedly%20exceeds%20%242%20billion.%20Meta%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20China%20and%20the%20US%20have%20long%20engaged%20in%20tit-for-tat%20regulatory%20exchanges%20involving%20their%20tech%20companies%2C%20analysts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20this%20probe%20is%20notable%20because%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20discouraging%20so-called%20%26quot%3BSingapore%20washing%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20process%20of%20moving%20a%20company%20from%20China%20to%20Singapore%20to%20reduce%20regulatory%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok's%20parent%20company%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20and%20fast-fashion%20giant%20Shein%20are%20among%20those%20that%20have%20shifted%20their%20headquarters%20from%20China%20to%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20is%20also%20a%20means%20to%20discourage%20Chinese%20AI%20startups%20from%20choosing%20the%20US%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20Beijing's%20probe%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20prevent%20the%20loss%20of%20AI%20technology%20and%20talent%20to%20foreign%20acquisition%2C%20especially%20to%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Wendy