0brightest.%20Last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpay-cuts-poaching-pivoting-inside-scale-ai-meta-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20invested%20%2414%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20AI%20training%20startup%20Scale%20AI%2C%20bringing%20its%20CEO%2C%20Alexandr%20Wang%2C%20over%20to%20run%20the%20tech%20giant's%20AI%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20Manus%20probe%20could%20signal%20that%20it%20was%20policing%20%26quot%3Boutbound%20AI%20technology%20transfer%20with%20greater%20rigor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grandhi%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20could%20accelerate%20the%20%26quot%3Bbifurcation%20of%20AI%20ecosystems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20China%20have%20been%20taking%20diverging%20approaches%20to%20AI%2C%20with%20Chinese%20companies%20tending%20to%20favor%20AI%20models%20that%20are%20more%20open%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-startup-deepseek-openai-america-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuch%20as%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20how%20long%20China's%20probe%20will%20last%2C%20should%20it%20progress%20into%20a%20full%20investigation.%20Other%20investigations%20from%20China's%20Ministry%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-nvidia-violated-antitrust-laws-mellanox-chips-semiconductors-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etaken%20more%20than%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrandhi%20said%20that%20in%20his%20view%2C%20the%20most%20likely%20outcome%20is%20that%20the%20deal%20will%20be%20approved%20%26quot%3Bwith%20constraints%2C%20rather%20than%20an%20outright%20block.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20outcome%20may%20be%2C%20this%20certainly%20sends%20a%20signal%20to%20other%20US%20or%20foreign%20companies%20that%20are%20considering%20similar%20acquisitions%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Dohmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt