xploration%20for%20three%20to%20four%20months%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20areas%20are%20ice-free%20enough%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20Poulsen%20said%20sites%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20get%20to%2C%20often%20requiring%20helicopters%20that%20push%20costs%20higher.%20There's%20rarely%20any%20infrastructure%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20build%20everything%20from%20scratch%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20mine%20to%20where%20workers%20will%20live.%20After%20all%20that%2C%20identifying%20a%20promising%20deposit%20can%20take%20years%2C%20sometimes%20decades%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Infrastructure%20at%20Lumina's%20Greenland%20mine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69612d2764858d02d218103b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20Lumina's%20Greenland%20mine.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20mining%20requires%20investors%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20wait%20years%20without%20returns%20and%20have%20a%20high%20tolerance%20for%20risk.%20Nathanielsen%20said%20Greenland%20lacks%20the%20domestic%20capital%20to%20fund%20that%20process%20and%20depends%20heavily%20on%20foreign%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20quite%20sobering%20in%20terms%20of%20trying%20to%20keep%20your%20providers%20of%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Kiernan%2C%20honorary%20chairman%20of%20Cordiant%20Capital%2C%20a%20Canadian%20multinational%20investment%20management%20firm%20and%20one%20of%20Lumina's%20major%20backing%20investors%2C%20told%20Andersen%20in%20July.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22James%20Kiernan%20in%20a%20blue%20blazer%20and%20red%20tie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69612d8e832e0ef1ead77c11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJames%20Kiernan%20is%20the%20honorary%20chairman%20of%20Cordiant%20Capital.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKiernan%20pointed%20to%20multiple%20examples%20of%20mines%20affected%20as%20market%20realities%20shifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20mine%20called%20Ruby%20that%20was%20open%2C%20and%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20find%20rubies.%20They%20were%20open%20and%20closed%20and%20open%20and%20closed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Greenland%20Ruby%20mine%20and%20describing%20the%20stop-start%20pattern%20that%20has%20defined%20many%20efforts%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254010e6e-9d6f-47b5-beb5-38513b3ffcc0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'One%20mine%20at%20a%20time'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20government%20has%20kept%20strict%20environmental%20and%20social%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20any%20project%20moves%20forward%2C%20Nathanielsen%20said%20companies%20must%20answer%20two%20questions%3A%20Will%20it%20create%20jobs%20for%20Greenlanders%2C%20and%20how%20will%20it%20protect%20the%20environment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20project%20owners%20cannot%20answer%20those%20two%20questions%20on%20a%20satisfactory%20level%2C%20if%20they%20cannot%20provide%20the%20people%20with%20a%20good%20answer%2C%20they%20will%20meet%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Truck%20driving%20near%20Lumina%20mine%20in%20Greenland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6961313164858d02d21810f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreenland's%20lush%20natural%20landscape%20in%20the%20background%20near%20Lumina's%20mine.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELumina's%20success%20in%20navigating%20that%20process%20is%20in%20part%20due%20to%20its%20long%20planning%20horizons%2C%20close%20coordination%20with%20the%20government%2C%20and%20a%20business%20model%20designed%20around%20Greenland's%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20mine%20has%20yet%20to%20turn%20a%20profit%2C%20Kiernan%20told%20Andersen%20during%20a%20follow-up%20call%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Bent%20Jensen%20and%20Kiernan%20said%20that%20after%20years%20of%20operating%20in%20Greenland's%20challenging%20conditions%2C%20the%20company%20is%20well-positioned%20to%20apply%20that%20know-how%20to%20other%20mining%20projects%2C%20and%20Lumina%20has%20recently%20secured%20an%20exploration%20license%20to%20search%20for%20rare%20earth%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20mines%20could%20unlock%20a%20new%20future%20for%20Greenlanders%2C%20helping%20pave%20a%20path%20toward%20greater%20autonomy%20as%20the%20island%20seeks%20to%20develop%20new%20revenue%20streams%20to%20eventually%20become%20financially%20independent%20from%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20mining%20boom%20isn't%20likely%20at%20any%20point%20soon%2C%20Bent%20Jensen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20Greenland%20developing%20slowly%20because%20it%20needs%20to%20develop%20organically%20with%20the%20population%2C%20with%20the%20politicians%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20one%20mine%20at%20a%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreenland-visit-mine-lumina-visit-only-fully-operational-anorthosite-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767991722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69612a6a64858d02d2180f94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreenland-visit-mine-lumina-visit-only-fully-operational-anorthosite-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Countries%20worldwide%20have%20eyes%20on%20Greenland%20for%20its%20natural%20resources%2C%20but%20the%20is