0Dyanmics'%20Atlas%20robot%20at%20CES%202026%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696130e504eda4732f2eca04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHyundai-owned%20Boston%20Dyanmics'%20Atlas%20robot%20at%20CES%202026.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELee%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHyundai%20Motor%20Group's%20booth%20had%20a%20really%20impressive%20display%20of%20how%20far%20it's%20trying%20to%20take%20autonomy%20%E2%80%94%20from%20EV%20charging%20stations%20and%20robotaxis%20to%20robotic%20arms%20and%20humanoid%20robots.%20Boston%20Dynamics%2C%20a%20Hyundai%20unit%2C%20demoed%20its%20Atlas%20humanoid%20robot%20at%20the%20booth.%20Just%20the%20way%20it%20activates%20and%20stands%20up%20is%20terrifying%20and%20awe-striking%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussolillo%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20cover%20robotaxis%20for%20BI%20and%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20test%20drive%20two%20different%20robotaxis%20this%20week.%20What%20stood%20out%20to%20you%20the%20most%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELee%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20tried%20two%20robotaxi%20services%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20including%20Amazon's%20Zoox.%20There%20are%20obviously%20a%20lot%20of%20smart%20people%20working%20on%20this%20technology.%20But%20I%20have%20to%20say%3A%20Trying%20those%20services%20only%20made%20me%20realize%201.)%20how%20far%20ahead%20Waymo%20is%20or%20at%20least%20appears%20to%20be%2C%20and%202.)%20just%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20make%20a%20profitable%20business%20case%20for%20robotaxis%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20autonomous%20driving%20right%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20challenge.%20There's%20also%20the%20operations%20side%20%E2%80%94%20like%20fleet%20scaling%20and%20management%20%E2%80%94%20that%20Waymo%20has%20had%20to%20build%20up%20to%20help%20make%20robotaxis%20feel%20like%20a%20real%20autonomous%20ride-hailing%20service%20you%20can%20use%20in%20your%20day-to-day.%20(That%20is%20if%20you%20live%20in%20the%20city%20Waymo%20operates.)%20And%20even%20then%2C%20we%20know%20Waymo%20is%20burning%20money%20on%20its%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224398%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robotaxi%20from%20Amazon's%20Zoox%20at%20the%20Consumer%20Electronics%20Show%20(CES)%202026%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69613063832e0ef1ead77c87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20robotaxi%20from%20Amazon's%20Zoox%20at%20CES%202026%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20T.%20Fallon%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussolillo%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20are%20some%20of%20the%20predictions%20you've%20heard%20from%20sources%20about%20tech%2C%20AI%20and%20business%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELee%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Chris%20Ahn%2C%20a%20principal%20at%20Deloitte%20with%20expertise%20in%20software-defined%20vehicles%2C%20had%20a%20few%20interesting%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20self-driving%20tech%20in%20personal%20vehicles%2C%20every%20automaker%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20chasing%20full%20autonomy%20the%20same%20way%20a%20Tesla%20or%20Rivian%20might.%20Instead%2C%20Ahn%20said%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20their%20customers%20want%20and%20what%20level%20of%20autonomy%20they%20think%20they'll%20need%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20an%20OEM%20and%20I%20know%20that%20most%20of%20my%20consumer%20bases%20are%20suburbanites%20that%20have%20two%20kids%20and%20families%20and%20things%20like%20that%20%E2%80%94%20what%20level%20of%20autonomy%20do%20I%20need%20for%20them%20and%20to%20achieve%20that%20level%20of%20autonomy%2C%20is%20it%20worth%20adding%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20LiDAR%20system%20to%20my%20bill%20of%20material%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAhn%20foresees%20a%20conversion%20happening%20between%20all%20of%20the%20emerging%20tech%20that's%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20past%20half%20decade.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20we're%20having%20separate%20conversations%20between%20humanoid%20robotics%2C%20generative%2Fagentic%20AI%2C%20and%20software-defined%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20all%20three%20of%20those%20terms%20are%20going%20to%20converge.%20My%20role%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20head%20of%20software-defined%20vehicles%20anymore.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20something%20like%20emerging%20technology%20or%20mobility%20tech.%20I%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussolillo%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20startup%20you%20never%20heard%20before%20really%20stole%20the%20show%20and%20impressed%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELee%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Perhaps%20less%20stole%20the%20show%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20Vay%2C%20a%20German%20startup%20developing%20a%20driverless%20car%20rental%20service%2C%20reminded%20me%20that%20there's%20still%20room%20for%20some%20contrarian%20voices%20in%20the%20driverless%20space.%20Remote%20driving%20is%20the%20big%20bogeyman%20for%20robotaxi%20companies.%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20caught%20using%20it.%20This%20startup's%20entire%20business%20model%20is%20built%20around%20it.%20Vay%20is%20using%20remote%20driving%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20potential%20to%20pursue%20autonomy%20in%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20overall%20driving%20experience%3A%20Getting%20the%20car%20delivered%20to%20a%20renter%20without%20a%20human%20inside.%20It%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BHuh%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20about%20that%26quot%3B%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Kia%20Vay%20remote-drive%20electric%20vehicle%20cruises%20during%20a%20live%20demonstration%20of%20remote%20driving%20on%20city%20streets%20ahead%20of%20the%20Consumer%20Electronics%20Show%20(CES).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696131a704eda4732f2eca2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224547%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Kia%20Vay%20remote-drive%20electric%20vehicle%20cruises%20during%20a%20live%20demonstration%20of%20remote%20driving%20on%20city%20streets.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20T.%20Fallon%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussolillo%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20did%20you%20learn%20that%20might%20change%20how%20you%20go%20about%20your%20tech%20coverage%20for%20BI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELee%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Broadly%2C%20emerging%20technologies%20like%20humanoid%20robots%2C%20self-driving%20cars%2C%20and%2C%20more%20generally%2C%20AI%2C%20contain%20a%20lot%20of%20unknowns%20and%20uncertainties.%20And%20company%20leaders%20in%20those%20spaces%20can%20be%20evasive%20when%20you%20ask%20for%20specifics%2C%20or%20they%20simply%20don't%20know%20the%20answer.%20Possibly%20both.%20My%20instinct%20is%20to%20resolve%20that%20ambiguity%2C%20which%20in%20this%20space%2C%20will%20not%20always%20be%20realistic.%20Instead%2C%20I%20should%20write%20%3Cem%3Eto%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20uncertainty%2C%20not%20through%20it.%20Name%20the%20ambiguity%2C%20build%20the%20story%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-ces-experience-robotaxis-humanoid-robots-ai-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767989855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69613bf204eda4732f2ecc27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-ces-experience-robotaxis-humanoid-robots-ai-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Robotaxi%20reporter%20Lloyd%20Lee%20breaks%20down%20what%20he%20saw%20%E2%80%94%20and%20heard%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20the%20world's%20largest%20consumer%20tech%20show%2C%20CES%2C%20in%20Vegas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%2