n%20Huang%20steps%20into%20the%20fray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fall%20of%20last%20year%2C%20AstraZeneca%20executive%20director%20Justin%20Johnson%20wrote%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20that%20while%20the%20DGX%20Spark%20met%20performance%20and%20speed%20claims%2C%20the%20software%20experience%20was%20buggy%20and%20unstable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20Nvidia%20executive%20shared%20Johnson's%20post%20in%20an%20internal%20email%20thread%2C%20Huang%20entered%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJump%20on%20x%20and%20say%20you%20will%20fix%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224341%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20founder's%20edition%20of%20the%20DGX%20Spark%20on%20display%20at%20a%20Paris%20tech%20show%20last%20June.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696134ce64858d02d21811b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223256%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20founder's%20edition%20of%20the%20DGX%20Spark%20on%20display%20at%20a%20Paris%20tech%20show%20last%20June.%3Cp%3EChesnot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20an%20Nvidia%20engineer%20replied%20that%20the%20company%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20Johnson%20to%20resolve%20most%20of%20the%20issues%2C%20which%20were%20related%20to%20a%20version%20mismatch%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fian-buck-nvidia-moat-cuda-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECUDA%2C%20Nvidia's%20software%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20allows%20developers%20to%20build%20AI%20apps%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowered%20by%20its%20GPUs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20responded%20that%20he%20appreciated%20the%20outreach%20and%20was%20exploring%20setting%20up%20DGX%20Spark%20at%20the%20pharmaceutical%20company%2C%20the%20chain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4b3712d-1e42-4b38-8c13-a0beceb23092%5C%22%3E